# Position C: LLM-evaluation PROMPTS are proprietary IP (the operationalization
# moat). This repo is PUBLIC — committing the prompts would publish the moat. So
# everything under prompts/ is gitignored EXCEPT the redacted example template and
# the README that document the contract.
#
# ⚠ The gitignored prompt files are therefore NOT repo-backed-up. Keep a durable
# backup of prompts/ OUTSIDE this repo (see prompts/README.md).
prompts/*
!prompts/_example.template.js
!prompts/README.md
